<div class="row">
  <div class="large-12 columns">
    <h1>Sarah and Jake's Registry</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">

  <div class="large-4 small-12 columns">
    <div class="panel">
      <div class="row">
        <p class="large-12 small-6 columns">
          <%= image_tag "couple.png" %>
        </p>

        <p class="large-12 small-6 columns">
          <strong>Our story:</strong> 5 years ago our eyes met across a crowded hostel common room and the rest is history! Since then we've shared countless adventures and we hope you'll join us as we embark on the biggest adventure of all... MARRIAGE!!
        </p>

        <p class="large-12 small-6 columns">
          <strong>Our project:</strong> We have decided that we want our wedding to make a difference in the world, so we've decided to sponsor building a classroom for a school in Tanzania through our wedding registry. Here you'll see a list of items that this project requires to get off the ground and we invite you to choose the items that you would like to purchase on our behalf.
        </p>

        <p class="large-12 small-6 columns"><strong>Organization:</strong> <a href="http://www.mufindiorphans.org/" target="_blank">Mufindi Orphans Project</a></p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <% if current_user && current_user.system_admin %>
      <% if @registry.approved_projects.empty? %>
        <%= link_to "Pending Projects", registry_project_path(:url_slug => @registry.url_slug), :class => 'button expand radius alert' %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "Approved Project", registry_project_path(:url_slug => @registry.url_slug), :class => 'button expand radius success' %>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="large-8 small-12 columns">

    <div class="panel">

      <div class="row">
        <h3 class="small-12 columns centered">Help us Build a Classroom in Tanzania!</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="row">

        <div class="medium-3 small-4 columns">
          <%= image_tag "mufindi_profile.png" %>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-6 small-8 columns">
          <p>Through the Mufindi Orphans Project, we're helping to build a classroom for a primary school in the Mhaji village in Tanzania. Below, you can select the specific materials you would like to contribute to the project as part of your wedding gift. Thanks!</p>
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/Mmhdj" target="_blank">Mufindi, Tanzania</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-3 hide-for-small columns">
          <div id="donut"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <%= form_for([@registry, @registry.orders.build]) do |f| %>

      <%= fields_for :items do |ff| %>
        <% @registry.item_types.each do |item_type| %>
          <div><%= item_type.name %></div>
          <div><%= item_type.items.available.count %></div>
          <%= ff.number_field(item_type.name, in: 0..item_type.items.available.count) %>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>

      <%= f.email_field(:email, placeholder: 'joe@joe.com') %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="small-12 columns">
          <%= submit_tag('Checkout') %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <div id="js-thank-you-modal" class="reveal-modal small thank-you-modal" data-reveal>
      <h2 id="thank-you">Thank You!</h2>
      <a href="#" class="close-reveal-modal">&times;</a>

      <div class="row">
        <p>Thanks so much for contributing to our special day by supporting the <strong>Mufindi Orphan Project</strong>! We can't wait to see you at the wedding!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-alert id="js-cart-success" class="alert-box success radius hidden">
      Items added to cart
      <a href="#" class="close">&times;</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
